arts.ttl: Pasveer own goal sees Ajax drop points against Utrecht
arts.sum: A late own goal earned FC Utrecht a 2-2 draw at Ajax on Wednesday evening. The game was initially meant to be played in September but police strikes meant that the game had to be moved.
